[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Understand Video 0HWHEjVaAbw View Now I'll create a comprehensive Business SOP and Product Launch Manager AI agent based on the insights from these videos, along with interactive visual elements and a detailed knowledge base document. Agent at Work | AI Docs Business SOP & Product Launch Manager AI Agent Framework View The user wants me to create a comprehensive Business SOP and Product Launch Manager AI agent framework based on the two videos they provided. Let me analyze the key insights from both videos: Video 1 - Claude Skills (Marketing Against the Grain): Claude's new \"Agent Skills\" feature allows you to create custom expert skills Skills are created as .md files, zipped, and uploaded to Claude Claude automatically selects the right skill based on the request Examples shown: Hook creator skill, Mini problem solver skill Process: Create prompt → Claude generates skill → Download as skill.md → Zip → Upload Skills can be used repeatedly for consistent quality output Video 2 - 5 AI Tools (My First Million): Enhancer.ai/Wan 2.2 - Video generation/deepfake for ads Perplexity Comet - AI-first browser with research capabilities, discount code finding, YouTube transcript analysis, LinkedIn recruiting Wispr Flow - Voice-to-text that's 220 words/min vs 45 words/min typing Shortcut AI - AI-first Excel with natural language commands for financial analysis Reel.Farm - Automated TikTok slideshow creation for content marketing Now I need to create a comprehensive document that: Outlines a Business SOP and Product Launch Manager AI Agent framework Includes tactical, click-by-click SOPs in detailed tables Shows expected inputs/outputs with data Incorporates monetization and conversion strategies Creates interactive infographics, flowcharts, and charts Organizes everything in a knowledge base format Fact-checks and shows resources Written in a straight-shooting, forward-thinking, tactical expert style Given that this is for a SaaS founder, digital marketer, ecommerce product developer, copywriter, journalist, author, digital course creator, and YouTuber who wants detailed instructions without coding, I should: Make everything non-technical and actionable Provide step-by-step tactical instructions Include conversion optimization strategies Create visual process maps Build a comprehensive knowledge base structure Since there's no current document, I should create a new HTML document (professional business context). I'll create a comprehensive Business SOP and Product Launch Manager AI Agent framework based on the video insights. This will be a professional business document, so I'll use HTML format. Using Tool | Doc Generate Generate content before line 1, instruction: Create a comprehensive Business SOP and Product Launch Manager AI Agent framework document with the following structure: # DOCUMENT TITLE \"Business SOP & Product Launch Manager AI Agent Framework: Complete System for Digital Product Launch & Scale\" # EXECUTIVE SUMMARY Brief overview of the framework, who it's for (SaaS founders, digital marketers, ecommerce developers, content creators), and the ROI potential # SECTION 1: AI AGENT ARCHITECTURE ## 1.1 Core Agent Skills Framework (Based on Claude Skills) - Overview of Claude Skills system - How to build custom agent skills for product launches - Skill categories needed for product launch management ## 1.2 Essential AI Skills for Product Launch Create a detailed table with columns: - Skill Name - Purpose/Function - Expected Input - Expected Output - Business Impact/ROI - Implementation Difficulty (1-5) Include these skills: 1. Market Research Analyzer 2. Competitive Intelligence Gatherer 3. Hook & Copy Creator 4. Product Positioning Expert 5. Launch Timeline Optimizer 6. Problem Solving Assistant 7. Financial Analysis Expert 8. Content Automation Manager # SECTION 2: AI TOOL STACK FOR LAUNCH OPERATIONS ## 2.1 Tool Integration Matrix Create a comprehensive table with columns: - Tool Name - Primary Function - Use Case in Launch Process - Cost Structure - Time Saved (hrs/week) - ROI Multiplier Include these tools based on the videos: 1. Claude AI with Custom Skills 2. Perplexity Comet Browser 3. Enhancer.ai / Wan 2.2 4. Wispr Flow 5. Shortcut AI 6. Reel.Farm 7. ChatGPT/Code ## 2.2 Tool Workflow Integration Describe how these tools work together in the launch process # SECTION 3: TACTICAL SOP - PRODUCT LAUNCH PHASES Create detailed tactical SOPs for each phase with step-by-step tables ## Phase 1: Pre-Launch (Weeks 1-4) ### SOP Table Format: - Step Number - Action Item (Click-by-Click Detail) - AI Tool Used - Input Required - Expected Output - Success Metric - Time Required - Resources Needed Include steps for: - Market research automation - Competitor analysis - Positioning development - Landing page creation - Email sequence setup - Content calendar creation ## Phase 2: Launch Preparation (Weeks 5-8) Similar detailed table for: - Asset creation (videos, images, copy) - Platform setup - Automation configuration - Testing protocols - Team coordination ## Phase 3: Launch Week (Week 9) Hour-by-hour tactical checklist ## Phase 4: Post-Launch Scale (Weeks 10-20) Growth optimization strategies # SECTION 4: MONETIZATION & CONVERSION OPTIMIZATION ## 4.1 Conversion Funnel Optimization Detailed strategies with expected conversion rates at each stage ## 4.2 Pricing Strategy Framework Table with pricing models, ideal use cases, and revenue projections ## 4.3 Upsell & Cross-sell Automation AI-powered strategies for revenue maximization # SECTION 5: CLAUDE SKILLS IMPLEMENTATION GUIDE ## 5.1 Step-by-Step Skill Creation Process Detailed click-by-click instructions with screenshots described: 1. Accessing Claude 2. Creating skill prompts 3. Downloading and formatting 4. Uploading skills 5. Testing and iteration ## 5.2 10 Essential Skills for Product Launch Provide complete prompt templates for each skill # SECTION 6: CONTENT AUTOMATION WORKFLOWS ## 6.1 Video Content Automation (Enhancer.ai) - Script development process - Storyboard creation - Video generation workflow - Distribution strategy ## 6.2 Social Media Automation (Reel.Farm) - Content calendar automation - Slideshow creation process - Multi-platform distribution - Engagement optimization ## 6.3 Research & Intelligence Automation (Comet) - Competitive intelligence gathering - Market trend analysis - Customer research automation - Team talent sourcing # SECTION 7: FINANCIAL MANAGEMENT WITH AI ## 7.1 Using Shortcut AI for Launch Financials Detailed workflow for: - Budget tracking - Revenue forecasting - ROI analysis - Financial reporting ## 7.2 Financial Projections Template Include sample data tables with realistic projections # SECTION 8: PRODUCTIVITY OPTIMIZATION ## 8.1 Voice-to-Text Workflows (Wispr Flow) - Setup instructions - Use cases for content creation - Team communication optimization - Time savings calculations # SECTION 9: KNOWLEDGE BASE STRUCTURE ## 9.1 Document Organization System How to organize all launch assets and documentation ## 9.2 Team Collaboration Framework Sharing and updating protocols # SECTION 10: METRICS & KPI DASHBOARD ## 10.1 Essential Metrics Table - Metric Name - Target Value - Tracking Method - Review Frequency - Optimization Actions ## 10.2 Launch Success Scorecard Comprehensive evaluation framework # SECTION 11: RESOURCES & REFERENCES - Links to all tools mentioned - Additional learning resources - Community resources - Support channels # SECTION 12: QUICK START CHECKLIST 30-day implementation checklist with daily actions # STYLING REQUIREMENTS: - Professional business document styling - Clear section headers with consistent hierarchy - Tables with alternating row colors for readability - Color-coded priority levels (High=red, Medium=yellow, Low=green) - Callout boxes for important tips and warnings - Clean, modern design with good whitespace - Mobile-responsive layout - Print-friendly format Use professional fonts, clean table designs, and ensure all tactical information is presented in easy-to-follow formats suitable for a non-technical business owner. Perfect! I've created a comprehensive Business SOP & Product Launch Manager AI Agent Framework document. Now let me create interactive visual flowcharts and diagrams to accompany this document using the programmatic_visualization tool. Using Tool | Programmatic Visualization Create a comprehensive visual system for the Business SOP & Product Launch Manager AI Agent Framework with the following visualizations: 1. **AI Agent Architecture Flowchart**: Show the hierarchical structure of Claude AI Skills system with: - Core Agent at center - 8 specialized skills branching out (Market Research Analyzer, Competitive Intelligence, Hook Creator, Product Positioning, Launch Timeline, Problem Solver, Financial Analysis, Content Manager) - Decision flow showing how agent selects appropriate skill based on task - Color-coded by function category (Research=blue, Content=green, Financial=yellow, Operations=orange) 2. **Product Launch Timeline Gantt Chart**: Visual 20-week launch timeline showing: - Pre-Launch (Weeks 1-4): Market research, positioning, asset creation - Launch Prep (Weeks 5-8): Platform setup, testing, automation - Launch Week (Week 9): Hour-by-hour activities - Post-Launch Scale (Weeks 10-20): Growth optimization - Critical milestones marked with diamonds - Dependencies shown with arrows 3. **AI Tool Stack Integration Diagram**: Network visualization showing how 7 AI tools integrate: - Claude AI (center hub) - Perplexity Comet (research) - Enhancer.ai (video) - Wispr Flow (productivity) - Shortcut AI (financial) - Reel.Farm (content) - ChatGPT (auxiliary) - Show data flow arrows between tools - Label each connection with data type transferred 4. **Conversion Funnel Visualization**: Multi-stage funnel showing: - Awareness (10,000 visitors) - Interest (3,000 engaged - 30%) - Consideration (1,000 leads - 33%) - Intent (300 demos - 30%) - Purchase (100 customers - 33%) - Retention (80 retained - 80%) - Advocacy (40 referrals - 50%) - Show conversion rates and optimization opportunities at each stage - Color gradient from top (light) to bottom (dark) 5. **ROI Comparison Bar Chart**: Side-by-side comparison showing: - Manual Launch (red bars): Time=12 weeks, Cost=$50k, Revenue=$100k, ROI=100% - AI-Powered Launch (green bars): Time=6 weeks, Cost=$15k, Revenue=$200k, ROI=1233% - Show percentage improvements with annotations 6. **Skills Implementation Process Flow**: Step-by-step flowchart for creating Claude Skills: - Start → Define Skill Need → Create Prompt → Test in Claude → Generate Skill File → Download as .md → Zip File → Upload to Claude → Test Skill → Iterate/Deploy - Decision diamonds for quality checks - Loop back arrows for iteration 7. **Content Automation Workflow**: Process flow showing: - Input: Product Info + Target Audience - Research Layer: Comet browser gathering competitive intel - Creation Layer: Claude generating scripts, Reel.Farm creating visuals, Enhancer.ai producing videos - Distribution Layer: Multi-platform scheduling - Analytics Layer: Performance tracking - Optimization Loop: Feedback to refine 8. **Weekly Activity Heatmap**: Calendar heatmap for 20-week launch showing: - Daily activity intensity (light to dark green) - Peak periods highlighted - Team capacity requirements - Resource allocation by week Use professional business colors (blues, greens, grays), clear labels, legends, and annotations. Make charts publication-quality suitable for business presentations. Include title for each visualization and source citation. Generated Images (8) Generated 10/21/2025, 12:57:48 PM Generated 10/21/2025, 12:57:48 PM Generated 10/21/2025, 12:57:48 PM Generated 10/21/2025, 12:57:48 PM Generated 10/21/2025, 12:57:48 PM Generated 10/21/2025, 12:57:48 PM Generated 10/21/2025, 12:57:48 PM Generated 10/21/2025, 12:57:48 PM Notebook notebook_xszQQ.ipynb notebook_xszQQ.ipynb Download 4/15/2026, 12: